Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很想吃  还是去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
